In[183]:
#recorte
citiesMexico_clipped = gpd.clip(gdf=cities, mask=mexico)
riversMexico_clipped = gpd.clip(gdf=rivers, mask=mexico)
In[184]:

                    ax=base)
riversMexico_clipped.plot(edgecolor='blue', linewidth=0.5,
                    ax=base)
